findings.title: Owner can update total buy tax less than 10%
findings.description: The contract owner has the capability to update the total buy tax to a value less than 10%, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can update total sell tax less than 10%
findings.description: The contract owner has the capability to update the total sell tax to a value less than 10%, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner cannot mint after initial deployment
findings.description: The contract owner loses the ability to mint new tokens after the initial deployment.

findings.title: Owner cannot burn
findings.description: The owner of the contract does not have the capability to burn tokens.

findings.title: Owner cannot block users
findings.description: The owner of the contract does not have the ability to block users.

findings.title: Owner cannot pause contract
findings.description: The owner of the contract does not have the ability to pause the contract.
